[32m│[0m #### **3. Application Functionality**                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The `/app` Flask application appears to be a **"Smart API Nanoservice"**     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m that:                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Acts as a configurable proxy/caller to backend APIs                        [32m│[0m
