[32m│[0m - **Nginx Root**: `http://nginx:80/`                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Flask App**: `http://flask_app:8080` → mapped to `http://nginx:80/app/`  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Flask API**: `http://flask_api:8081` → mapped to `http://nginx:8081/`    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **3. API Functionality:**                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/api/get` and `/api/set?url=` - Manages a URL value (default:             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `http://flask_api:8081/script`)                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/name/get` and `/name/set?name=` - Manages a name value (default:         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `Cocomelon`)                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **4. Potential Attack Vectors:**                                             [32m│[0m
